    "name": "Leap Galaxy",
    "steam_appid": 3327880,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/add735ec4455efcf99dc52e1ce0d8518.poster.avif?t=1752800947\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/add735ec4455efcf99dc52e1ce0d8518.webm?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/add735ec4455efcf99dc52e1ce0d8518.mp4?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leap Galaxy is a 2D platformer with a minimalist aesthetic and gameplay that puts speed and flow first. Take advantage of momentum and master the recoil of your shots to reach insane speeds and beat each level as fast as posible!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Master unique and creative mechanics</strong> that redefine how you move through space. Each world introduces a fresh twist on movement and momentum.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore 8 handcrafted worlds</strong>, each packed with distinct environments, obstacles, challenges and secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn stars</strong> by clearing levels quickly, and spend them to unlock new characters and color palettes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race</strong> against ghost replays of top players and learn from the best.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Climb the leaderboards</strong>, competing with friends and players around the globe.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/f19ad2cab407fb1e9a48e6165845b527.poster.avif?t=1752800947\" width=618 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/f19ad2cab407fb1e9a48e6165845b527.webm?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/f19ad2cab407fb1e9a48e6165845b527.mp4?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New ways to move</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each world introduces a unique movement mechanic that completely changes how you navigate its levels, from speed rings and gravity zones to railings and teleportation lines. Every mechanic expands your movement possibilities, allowing you to move lightning fast through the levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/eecb622670249ce847145fa00b64d00c.poster.avif?t=1752800947\" width=618 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/eecb622670249ce847145fa00b64d00c.webm?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/eecb622670249ce847145fa00b64d00c.mp4?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Every second counts</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Leap Galaxy, speed is everything. If you want to collect all stars you’ll need to fly through the levels and set new records. Compete with players across the globe in every planet’s final challenge, where you’ll have to go through all the world’s levels back to back and fight for a spot on the online leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/47788e55359fe2d2e9299479bf3181a9.poster.avif?t=1752800947\" width=618 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/47788e55359fe2d2e9299479bf3181a9.webm?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/47788e55359fe2d2e9299479bf3181a9.mp4?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Race &amp; replay mode!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to improve your times even further? Watch replays from anyone on the leaderboards and learn their strategies! Race alongside their <strong>replay</strong> <strong>ghosts</strong> and push your skills to the limit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/675c79e3d8b2aecb04b388d6c4ac8f11.poster.avif?t=1752800947\" width=618 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/675c79e3d8b2aecb04b388d6c4ac8f11.webm?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/675c79e3d8b2aecb04b388d6c4ac8f11.mp4?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Leap in style</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock a wide variety of playable characters, each with their own distinct and charming animations. Not a fan of the default colors? No worries, we got you covered! Choose between a variety of unlockable color schemes to match your style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/24fe7bcb6e06db5bfc02feb070e16c02.poster.avif?t=1752800947\" width=618 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/24fe7bcb6e06db5bfc02feb070e16c02.webm?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327880/extras/24fe7bcb6e06db5bfc02feb070e16c02.mp4?t=1752800947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
